    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Disc Golf</strong> is a casual local multiplayer game for 1–4 players that brings the fun of the outdoor sport to your screen. Choose from 10 unique characters, each with their own stats, and play across 10 scenic courses using a wide selection of discs with distinct flight characteristics. Disc flights are inspired by real-world physics, so speed, glide, turn, and fade all matter. Plan your shots, master each character’s strengths, and compete with friends for the lowest score.</p>",
